Also any messages displayed in the bar below the EC database area should contain relevant and clear messages
e.g.•Dynamic scan•Problem messages for resources etc.Also during the duration/scanning of EC’s attention should
be paid to the bottom left scanning area to ensure that the information and data displayed there is correct.
